::Aerotaur::
       He scratches his head and nods.  "Hi there.  Would you like a tour of 
the base, or some quarters."  He smirks.  "We were under attack for a while 
but they all seem to have left."  He shrugs.  "We aren't exactly the most 
liked faction on the planet but we're righteous and noble.  If there's 
anything else you need just ask."
